events.title: Prancing for Prosthetics
events.description: The inaugural Prancing for Prosthetics event that started our annual holiday tradition of combining fitness, festive spirit, and fundraising. This first-ever 5K run/walk demonstrated the strong community support that would become a hallmark of AFL events.

gallery.alt: Large group photo of participants at the First Annual Prancing for Prosthetics event, wearing winter gear and holiday accessories on a rainy day

historical.significance: First running event organized by Aggies for Limbs
historical.legacy: Established the tradition of our annual holiday-themed 5K fundraiser
